## 3 / 8

**EN:** Real tech stack:

• `secp256k1 DIDs` → Sovereign identity (no Google, no Apple)
• `Kademlia DHT (XOR) over UDP` → Decentralized routing
• `CRDTs + BadgerDB` → Offline-first state with atomic merges
• `Noise Framework (ChaCha20-Poly1305)` → Encrypted tunnels with real NAT traversal
• `Dynamic PoW + reputation` → Adaptive anti-Sybil

**ES:** Stack técnico real:

• `DIDs secp256k1` → Identidad soberana (sin Google ni Apple)
• `Kademlia DHT (XOR) sobre UDP` → Ruteo descentralizado
• `CRDTs + BadgerDB` → Estado offline-first con merges atómicos
• `Noise Framework (ChaCha20-Poly1305)` → Túneles cifrados con NAT traversal real
• `PoW dinámico + reputación` → Anti-Sybil adaptativo

